                "file_text": "# RIDSR Project - Quick Reference Checklist\n**Start Date:** February 12, 2026  \n**Target Completion:** February 27, 2026 (12 working days)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Models ✅ (Days 1-2)\n\n### Day 1\n- [ ] Simplify Patient.ts (15 → 9 fields)\n- [ ] Simplify Case.ts (16 → 10 fields)\n- [ ] Simplify User.ts (10 → 8 fields)\n- [ ] Review Facility.ts\n\n### Day 2\n- [ ] Create migration script\n- [ ] Update type definitions\n- [ ] Run migration\n- [ ] Test models\n\n**Deliverable:** Simplified models with 40% fewer fields\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Services ✅ (Days 3-4)\n\n### Day 3\n- [ ] Create `/src/lib/services/server/` directory\n- [ ] Implement BaseService class\n- [ ] Refactor caseService to server-side\n\n### Day 4\n- [ ] Refactor patientService\n- [ ] Refactor userService\n- [ ] Refactor facilityService\n- [ ] Delete old client-side services\n\n**Deliverable:** Server-side services with proper separation\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: API Routes ✅ (Days 5-7)\n\n### Day 5\n- [ ] Create API response wrapper\n- [ ] Create validation middleware\n- [ ] Create Zod schemas\n- [ ] Refactor /api/cases\n\n### Day 6\n- [ ] Refactor /api/patients\n- [ ] Refactor /api/users\n- [ ] Refactor /api/facilities\n- [ ] Add search endpoints\n\n### Day 7\n- [ ] Test all API endpoints\n- [ ] Test validation\n- [ ] Test error handling\n- [ ] Test pagination\n\n**Deliverable:** Standardized API with consistent responses\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: UI & Forms ✅ (Days 8-9)\n\n### Day 8\n- [ ] Refactor SearchableSelect (add generics, async, multi-select)\n- [ ] Update CaseReportForm (use SearchableSelect for patient)\n\n### Day 9\n- [ ] Update UserManagementForm\n- [ ] Update FacilityManagementForm\n- [ ] Create form examples documentation\n\n**Deliverable:** Enhanced SearchableSelect, simplified forms\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Integration ✅ (Days 10-12)\n\n### Day 10\n- [ ] Integration testing (all flows)\n- [ ] Bug fixing (high priority)\n\n### Day 11\n- [ ] Bug fixing (medium/low priority)\n- [ ] Performance optimization\n\n### Day 12\n- [ ] Documentation\n- [ ] Code review & cleanup\n- [ ] Final testing\n\n**Deliverable:** Production-ready system\n\n---\n\n## Critical Files to Modify\n\n### Models (6 files)\n- [ ] `/src/lib/models/Patient.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/lib/models/Case.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/lib/models/User.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/lib/models/Facility.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/lib/models/Alert.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/lib/models/index.ts`\n\n### Services (5 files to create)\n- [ ] `/src/lib/services/server/baseService.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/lib/services/server/caseService.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/lib/services/server/patientService.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/lib/services/server/userService.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/lib/services/server/facilityService.ts`\n\n### API Routes (8 files)\n- [ ] `/src/app/api/cases/route.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/app/api/patients/route.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/app/api/patients/search/route.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/app/api/users/route.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/app/api/facilities/route.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/app/api/facilities/search/route.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/lib/api/response.ts` (new)\n- [ ] `/src/lib/schemas/index.ts` (update)\n\n### Forms (4 files)\n- [ ] `/src/components/ui/SearchableSelect.tsx`\n- [ ] `/src/components/forms/CaseReportForm.tsx`\n- [ ] `/src/components/forms/UserManagementForm.tsx`\n- [ ] `/src/components/forms/FacilityManagementForm.tsx`\n\n### Types (2 files)\n- [ ] `/src/types/index.ts`\n- [ ] `/src/types/forms.ts`\n\n---\n\n## Key Improvements Summary\n\n### Before → After\n\n**Patient Model:**\n- 15 fields → 9 fields (40% reduction)\n- Complex address → Single district field\n- Multiple timestamps → Single createdAt\n\n**Case Model:**\n- 16 fields → 10 fields (37.5% reduction)\n- Computed fields removed\n- Lab results moved to separate collection\n\n**User Model:**\n- 10 fields → 8 fields (20% reduction)\n- Province removed (derive from district)\n\n**Services:**\n- Client-side fetch → Server-side database operations\n- No validation → Zod validation\n- Inconsistent errors → Standardized error handling\n\n**API Routes:**\n- Raw responses → Wrapped in ApiResponse\n- No validation → Zod validation on all routes\n- Generic errors → Specific error messages\n- No pagination → Pagination support\n\n**Forms:**\n- Text inputs → SearchableSelect components\n- Static options → Async data loading\n- 15+ fields → Max 10 fields\n- Inconsistent validation → Unified validation\n\n**SearchableSelect:**\n- Basic → Full-featured\n- No types → Generic types\n- Sync only → Async support\n- Single select → Multi-select support\n\n---\n\n## Success Criteria\n\n### Must Have ✅\n- [ ] Zero TypeScript errors\n- [ ] All forms submit successfully\n- [ ] All API endpoints return consistent responses\n- [ ] SearchableSelect works with async data\n- [ ] Models have 40% fewer fields\n- [ ] All tests pass\n\n### Should Have ⚠️\n- [ ] Page load < 2 seconds\n- [ ] API response < 500ms\n- [ ] Code coverage > 70%\n- [ ] Documentation complete\n\n### Nice to Have 💡\n- [ ] Performance monitoring\n- [ ] Error tracking\n- [ ] Analytics integration\n\n---\n\n## Daily Standup Questions\n\n1. What did I complete yesterday?\n2. What will I work on today?\n3. Any blockers or issues?\n4. Am I on track with the schedule?\n\n---\n\n## Emergency Contacts\n\n**If stuck:**\n1. Check FILE_BY_FILE_ANALYSIS.md for detailed file info\n2. Check IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md for task details\n3. Check ANALYSIS_REPORT.md for overall context\n\n**If critical bug:**\n1. Document the bug\n2. Check if it blocks other work\n3. Fix immediately if blocking\n4. Otherwise, add to bug list\n\n---\n\n## Quick Commands\n\n```bash\n# Start development server\nnpm run dev\n\n# Run tests\nnpm test\n\n# Run linting\nnpm run lint\n\n# Build for production\nnpm run build\n\n# Run migration\nnpm run migrate\n\n# Create backup\nnpm run backup\n```\n\n---\n\n## Progress Tracking\n\nUpdate this section daily:\n\n### Week 1\n- **Day 1 (Mon):** ⬜ Models - Patient & Case\n- **Day 2 (Tue):** ⬜ Models - Migration & Testing\n- **Day 3 (Wed):** ⬜ Services - Structure & Case\n- **Day 4 (Thu):** ⬜ Services - Patient, User, Facility\n- **Day 5 (Fri):** ⬜ API - Infrastructure & Cases\n\n### Week 2\n- **Day 6 (Mon):** ⬜ API - Patients, Users, Facilities\n- **Day 7 (Tue):** ⬜ API - Testing\n- **Day 8 (Wed):** ⬜ UI - SearchableSelect & CaseForm\n- **Day 9 (Thu):** ⬜ UI - User & Facility Forms\n- **Day 10 (Fri):** ⬜ Integration - Testing & Bugs\n\n### Week 3\n- **Day 11 (Mon):** ⬜ Integration - Bugs & Performance\n- **Day 12 (Tue):** ⬜ Integration - Docs & Final Testing\n\n---\n\n## Notes Section\n\nUse this space for daily notes, issues, or reminders:\n\n```\nDate: ___________\nNotes:\n- \n- \n- \n\nIssues:\n- \n- \n\nCompleted:\n- \n- \n```\n\n---\n\n## Final Checklist Before Deployment\n\n- [ ] All TypeScript errors resolved\n- [ ] All tests passing\n- [ ] All linting errors fixed\n- [ ] Documentation complete\n- [ ] Environment variables set\n- [ ] Database migrated\n- [ ] Backup created\n- [ ] Performance tested\n- [ ] Security reviewed\n- [ ] Error handling tested\n- [ ] User acceptance testing done\n\n---\n\n**Ready to start? Begin with Phase 1, Day 1! 🚀**\n",
